PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of CAROLINE BELZILE of St-Elzéar, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Marie-Andrée Mallette.
